            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the kidney beans are in the oven, dissolve the<strong> beef stock mix</strong> in 350ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> ground cinnamon</strong> to the red onion and cook for 1 min</p>",
      "order": 4,
